# Cursor Rules — LinkHive

This project context lives in `.ai/`. Read `.ai/AGENTS.md` first before making any changes.

## TL;DR Rules for Cursor

- State management: flutter_bloc ONLY — no setState for business logic
- DI: get_it via locator.dart — never instantiate services in widgets
- Routing: go_router with MyRouteName constants — no Navigator.push
- Commands: always prefix `flutter` with `fvm` (e.g. `fvm flutter run`)
- Every screen has a Bloc (event/state/bloc files in a bloc/ subdirectory)
- Run `fvm flutter analyze` — must be zero warnings before committing
- Never hardcode route paths — use MyRouteName.xxx constants

